Package camp

Interface IIncreaseCampSlots

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CampStudentSlotIncreaser
    public interface IIncreaseCampSlots
    Represents an interface to increase the remaining number of camp slots of a camp in a database.

    2023-11-17
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Soo Qi Yang, Teo Kai Xuan, Masagca Merwyn Louie Dumasis, Nguyen Phuong Linh, Tee Jeeng Yee

      void increaseCampSlots​(String CampName)

    • Method Detail

      • increaseCampSlots

        void increaseCampSlots​(String CampName)
        Increases a camp's remaining number of slots. Implementing classes should take in a camp name and increment the remaining number slots, for the corresponding camp in the camp database, be it camp committee, attendee, total, or others.
        Parameters:
        CampName - The camp to have its slots reduced.
